ctive_commands"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"color":"#94a3b8"},"children":["→ handler: ",["$","span",null,{"style":{"color":"#ef4444"},"children":"BLOCKED"}]," (never invoked)"]}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"color":"#94a3b8"},"children":["→ blunder logged: ",["$","span",null,{"style":{"color":"#e2e8f0"},"children":"agent-blunders.json"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"marginTop":"8px","color":"#ef4444"},"children":"🚫 Mergen policy gate blocked this tool call."}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"marginTop":"4px","color":"#94a3b8"},"children":[["$","span",null,{"style":{"color":"#e2e8f0"},"children":"Why:"}]," Local Gate: Destructive command pattern matched."]}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"marginTop":"4px","color":"#94a3b8"},"children":[["$","span",null,{"style":{"color":"#4ade80"},"children":"What to do instead:"}]," Run `terraform plan -destroy` to preview"]}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"color":"#94a3b8"},"children":"  the blast radius, then request human approval before proceeding."}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"marginTop":"8px","color":"#666"},"children":"# agent reformulates → calls analyze_runtime → requests HITL approval"}],["$","div",null,{"style":{"color":"#4ade80"},"children":"✅ Handler runs within policy."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div","02",{"className":"feature-card","style":{"gridColumn":"8 / span 5","marginTop":"5rem"},"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"feature-icon","children":"🧑‍💻"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"feature-num","children":"02"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"feature-title","children":"Human-in-the-Loop (HITL) — Held Promise Approval"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"feature-desc","children":["For flagged-but-not-blocked calls (schema migrations, high blast-radius commands), the gate"," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"highlight-blue","children":"holds the Promise until a human approves or denies"}],". An outbound webhook fires to Slack or any HTTP endpoint with approve/deny URLs. The AI IDE blocks — MCP stdio is naturally async, so it waits indefinitely for the JSON-RPC response. No polling. No re-submission. One click resolves the hold.",["$","div",null,{"style":{"marginTop":"2rem","background":"#0f0f0f","border":"1px solid #2a2a2a","borderRadius":"8px","padding":"16px","fontFamily":"var(--font-geist-mono), monospace","fontSize":"0.72rem","lineHeight":1.8},"children":["$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d"]}]]}]]}],"$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31","$L32","$L33"]}]]}]
